1100
01:02:22,947 --> 01:02:24,990
- Tae-seop.
- Yeah?

1101
01:02:31,205 --> 01:02:34,416
I don't just like you.

1102
01:02:34,625 --> 01:02:36,752
I love you deeply.

1103
01:02:37,544 --> 01:02:41,173
How do you always know and prepare
exactly what I need?

1104
01:02:41,382 --> 01:02:43,425
Because I'm always watching you.

1105
01:02:43,717 --> 01:02:45,928
