1107
01:02:47,721 --> 01:02:50,266
- I'm calling the cops! Three!
- Three.

1108
01:02:50,391 --> 01:02:51,600
Hi, Sae-byeok.

1109
01:02:51,684 --> 01:02:54,436
Let's build a relationship
the way we want.

1110
01:02:54,895 --> 01:02:57,273
I couldn't stop thinking about you,
so here I am.

1111
01:02:58,023 --> 01:03:00,025
I'm glad we met now.

1112
01:03:05,197 --> 01:03:06,657
I like you.

1113
01:03:06,991 --> 01:03:09,451
I like you, too.

1114
01:03:09,535 --> 01:03:11,287
You can't sleep here!

1115
01:03:21,839 --> 01:03:22,881
Tae-seop

1116
